    "sourceText": "'cartridge \"CANADA FLAG/AMY STUDIO/2026\"\n\nconst Red = 6\nconst White = 15\n\nu8 Row = 0\nu8 LeftX = 0\nu8 RightX = 0\nu8 Y = 0, X = 0\nu8 HalfWidth = 0\n\n' Stylized Canadian flag for ColecoVision Mode 3.\n' The leaf is simplified to survive the 64x48 multicolor pixel grid.\n  multicolor screen\n  cls\n\n  ' CRT-safe two-pixel left padding.\n  box 2,5 to 16,41 color Red\n  box 17,5 to 48,41 color White\n  box 49,5 to 63,41 color Red\n\n  ' Maple leaf silhouette, drawn as horizontal red spans.\n  restore LeafRows\n  for Y = 11 to 32\nNextXHalfWidth:\n    read X\n    read HalfWidth\n    LeftX = 33 - X\n    RightX = 32 - X + HalfWidth\n    box LeftX,Y to RightX,Y color Red\n    LeftX = 33 + X - HalfWidth\n    RightX = 32 + X\n    box LeftX,Y to RightX,Y color Red\n    if X >= HalfWidth goto NextXHalfWidth\n  next\n\n  ' Stem.\n  box 32,33 to 33,37 color Red\n\n  screen on\n  loop forever\n\ndata LeafRows bytes\n  0,1\n  0,1\n  1,2\n  4,1,2,3\n  4,2,2,3\n  4,5\n  3,4\n  6,1,3,4\n  11,2,7,2,3,4\n  10,6,2,3\n  10,11\n  10,11\n  9,10\n  11,12\n  10,11\n  9,10\n  8,9\n  7,8\n  6,7\n  5,6\n  4,5\n  5,3,0,1\n  6,2,0,1\nend data"
